description:
Our Clients are looking at working in a variety of industries where they will be in contact with the public who have mental health issues.  

      They some relevant industry experience and qualifications but they have no Mental Health qualifications or awareness training.  So therefore would like to gain a Mental Health First Aid qualification.  

      Service Provider must:
      o include the price of transport within the quote;
      o deliver from a location in the Black Country that is accessible by public transport, outlining the planned delivery locations and venues to be used during the course;
      o adhere to health and safety rules and regulations being fully responsible for all risk assessments including external activities; provide PPE where necessary and report any accidents/incidents in a timely manner;
      o report on performance against agreed targets at a timeframe to be agreed and specified in the contract.

