description:
Pursuant to Reg. 58 of the Utilities Contracts Regulations 2016, Portsmouth Water Limited (&quot;PW&quot;) is hosting a Supply Chain Engagement Event on 25.03.2020 to raise market awareness of the potential opportunities associated with its Havant Thicket Reservoir project (&quot;Project&quot;) and to start its pre-procurement supply chain engagement exercise.  Please use the following link to register for the Supply Chain Engagement Event https://portsmouthwater.delta-esourcing.com/respond/8QJW68G5PR.

      It is envisaged that the Project will be delivered through various packages of contracts, including both works and services contracts. The main scope of the Project includes the design and construction of: 
      (i)Main reservoir works;
      (ii)Pipeline works;
      (iii)MEICA works;
      (iv)Pumping station upgrades; 
      (v)Pre-treatment facility;
      (vi)Visitor centre; 
      (vii)Environmental mitigation works; and
      (viii)Other associated works.

